{"tid":2447223,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【加密貨幣】印度擬禁止交易 6個月內要出清","createTime":"2021-03-15T05:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T12:13:01.000Z","uid":15564,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb805b7a302d74e4346927947429cd20c447f97","tid":2447223,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2901327/【加密貨幣】印度擬禁止交易%20%20%206個月內要出清\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2901327%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E3%80%91%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%93%AC%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%2520%2520%25206%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E6%B8%85&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ec52910d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2901327/【加密貨幣】印度擬禁止交易%20%20%206個月內要出清</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2901327/150321_16_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2901327%2F150321_16_600.jpg&h=ae9f8b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年加密貨幣價格不斷攀升，吸引了不少投資者目光。但最近在印度則傳出壞消息，印度政府擬立例禁止於印度交易加密貨幣，消息更指將不容許持有加密貨幣。若政策一旦落實，外界料將對數百萬加密貨幣投資者造成打擊。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述印度政府消息人士報道，該法案將會是世界上目前為止，所有針對加密貨幣的法案中最嚴厲的一個。法案將擁有、發行、採礦、交易以及轉讓加密貨幣等行為一律定義為犯罪。該措施符合印度政府1月份，要求禁止私人虛擬貨幣，如全球最大型的加密貨幣Bitcoin等交易，並建立官方數字貨幣交易框架。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，法案將容許加密貨幣持有者最多6個月時間，出售手上資產。若限期後依然持有，則會被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n現時印度總理莫迪（Narendra Modi）的政府在國會中佔有多數席位，官員有信心該法案將獲得通過。如果禁令實施，印度將成為首個將持有加密貨幣定義為非法的主要經濟體。現時中國雖然禁止採礦和交易加密貨幣，但亦不會懲罰持有者。<br />\n<br />\n據加密貨幣業內人士估算，目前印度共有800萬名加密貨幣投資者，擁有的資產達14億美元（約108億港元）。<br />\n<br />\nBitcoin於上周六（13日）創下了6萬美元（約46.8萬港元）的歷史高位，原因是獲得Tesla行政總裁馬斯（Elon Musk）等名人支持，使用加密貨幣交易的接受程度有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：李俊儀"},{"pid":"3bf338705b8a5a62617b1b7c41dcf2aecdc68c31","tid":2447223,"uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"唔好再升啦<br />\n55-57個時走左7成btc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc9af927623d45ff0c743e5d08f5fcbabf6e28a","tid":2447223,"uid":10336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"點查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d57fc59e62ad9b573b48b1c3c750e3675442af","tid":2447223,"uid":83228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"技術上 佢做到乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5b39492d0e0054f5326cb57f0cbae7dc236039","tid":2447223,"uid":215755,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:14:57.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我正價display card<br />\n礦狗不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f804e83d7eafac11c9963777b87351ed426fde3c","tid":2447223,"uid":5967,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"你知閪我有冇持有啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49b004d504e8ddb31f34db2fedcf10dd81e7abd","tid":2447223,"uid":170335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"64走晒riot<br />\n有機入貨了"},{"pid":"dd3d69520db0c0c306c8a4c11960750a1c73ca8f","tid":2447223,"uid":385809,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f804e83d7eafac11c9963777b87351ed426fde3c","tid":2447223,"uid":5967,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"你知閪我有冇持有啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"ban 晒所有交易所都死得啦<br />\n淨返用 cold wallet 現金交易<br />\n你驚唔驚比咖哩佬殺人搶貨 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{